<body>
    <h1>New Version v1.0.0</h1>
    <h2>Changelog</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Added SecureCRT session import (supports XML export).</li>
        <li>Introduced Distributed Mode (SocketProxy) for secure WebSocket-based connections via bastion hosts.</li>
        <li>Added quick WebSocket URL configuration for client/server connections.</li>
        <li>Standalone Mode: connect directly using Session Manager or Quick Connect.</li>
        <li>Integrated SFTP Browser with Direct, TCP Forward, and WebSocket Proxy support (basic upload/download).</li>
        <li>Command Broadcast: send commands to all active sessions simultaneously.</li>
        <li>
            Advanced Tab Management:
            <ol type="a">
                <li>Double-click to duplicate</li>
                <li>Middle-click to close</li>
                <li>Right-click for more options</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
            Secure Data Management:
            <ol type="a">
                <li>Non-sensitive settings saved in Windows Registry</li>
                <li>Passwords stored in Windows Credential Manager</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
    </ol>
</body>
</html>
